WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.792
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.816 --> 01:30.602
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 15=

01:30.602 --> 01:34.856
(That's because we met in the winter.)

01:34.856 --> 01:36.677
Eat these.

01:39.256 --> 01:40.597
This is good.

01:44.177 --> 01:46.336
- We have to listen to Mr. Mo to eat.
- Definitely.

01:46.336 --> 01:47.197
Thank you.

01:47.197 --> 01:54.157
If it's too spicy, add some vinegar.
I just heard you say it was spicy.

01:55.297 --> 01:56.716
Okay, thanks.

01:57.496 --> 01:58.177
That's enough.

01:58.177 --> 01:58.697
It's enough.

01:58.697 --> 01:59.716
Thanks.

02:05.297 --> 02:08.996
I'm also spiced out. It's so spicy.
Can you pour me some too?

02:10.096 --> 02:11.637
Should I give you a cup?

02:11.637 --> 02:14.857
No wonder you were dumped
with such a bad attitude.

02:14.857 --> 02:21.677
Our breakup was peaceful. Men shouldn't
speak ill of their exes, understand?

02:22.737 --> 02:23.797
Well said.

02:23.797 --> 02:25.436
Are you single?

02:28.776 --> 02:29.597
Single.

02:29.597 --> 02:32.177
I've heard online
that you have a girlfriend.

02:32.177 --> 02:36.036
That's all gossip and rumors
they fabricated and spread.

02:37.096 --> 02:38.717
Who did it? Clarify.

02:38.717 --> 02:41.956
I saw that post. Wasn't that
a girl called Shanshan?

02:41.956 --> 02:42.517
What?

02:42.517 --> 02:45.817
She was wrapped around your arm
in the photo, smiling so sweetly.

02:45.817 --> 02:47.477
Don't you know he's single?

02:48.137 --> 02:48.697
I meant to.

02:48.697 --> 02:50.837
Who told you?
You can't just blabber, you know.

02:50.837 --> 02:52.297
I told you to stop talking nonsense.

02:52.297 --> 02:53.836
Getting anxious now.

02:55.816 --> 02:58.477
Mr. Juemei is really nice.

02:58.477 --> 03:02.677
Sheng, do you have
any suitable single friends around you?

03:04.376 --> 03:06.077
Around me?

03:13.096 --> 03:15.237
Why? You look down on him?

03:19.737 --> 03:24.917
No. I-I-I don't want
a boyfriend for now.

03:26.977 --> 03:31.637
I can tell, you're single too.
Why don't you want a boyfriend?

03:36.977 --> 03:38.417
Why? I'm not done eating.

03:38.417 --> 03:41.637
I'll get you more soup so you won't be
thirsty from talking too much.

03:44.936 --> 03:46.837
Sorry for keeping you waiting.

03:46.837 --> 03:47.837
Let's take a picture.

03:47.837 --> 03:49.137
(Passenger Port)
Quite a long line.

03:49.137 --> 03:50.657
- He's here.
- Mr. Zhu is here.

03:50.657 --> 03:54.797
Let me introduce this to you.
We'll be taking a cruise

03:54.797 --> 03:59.996
across the river from this dock later.
Soon we'll see the famous Lijiang River.

03:59.996 --> 04:05.677
It's mentioned in many literary works,
like "stretches of green mountains".

04:05.677 --> 04:11.777
We can also see the pattern at the back
of the 20-yuan bill here. Let's go.

04:11.777 --> 04:18.457
I bought first-class seats for you.
We can sit at the bow to enjoy the view.

04:18.457 --> 04:20.177
- Thanks.
- You're so nice, Mr. Zhu.

04:20.177 --> 04:21.136
Thanks.

04:21.136 --> 04:22.317
I take it.

04:22.317 --> 04:24.077
Such an expense.

04:24.077 --> 04:28.717
I-I-I get seasick.
Is there another way to go?

04:28.717 --> 04:32.377
You get seasick? Even on a large cruise?

04:32.377 --> 04:37.157
I've been seasick since childhood.
Once I get on board, I'm dizzy and puke.

04:37.157 --> 04:40.077
You can go by car. We have cars.

04:40.656 --> 04:43.937
Many bad sailors choose to go by land.
The scenery along the way is good, too.

04:43.937 --> 04:46.877
Well, I'm going to take the car.

04:48.096 --> 04:49.416
Then I will accompany you.

04:49.416 --> 04:51.137
It's okay. I can manage on my own.

04:51.137 --> 04:52.596
Let me accompany you.

04:53.536 --> 04:56.437
Otherwise, you will ride so long alone
without anyone with you.

04:56.976 --> 04:59.536
Then you can't enjoy
the scenery by boat.

04:59.536 --> 05:01.716
That's okay for me.

05:02.497 --> 05:03.457
Alright, it's settled.

05:03.457 --> 05:06.597
Let Zhou Zheng keep you company.
At least you'll have someone to talk to.

05:06.597 --> 05:09.457
I'm okay, really. You go take your boat.
I can truly handle it alone.

05:09.457 --> 05:13.256
I'll accompany you, alright? I come here
often, but it's your first time.

05:13.256 --> 05:18.577
You accompany me. We haven't seen
each other for so long. Go with me.

05:18.577 --> 05:20.057
Return your ticket to me.

05:20.057 --> 05:21.557
Give me.

05:23.096 --> 05:27.276
Juemei, as the elder,
you take care of her for us.

05:28.176 --> 05:30.017
Let's go.

05:30.017 --> 05:31.037
Accompany us.

05:31.037 --> 05:32.317
Go.

05:33.497 --> 05:35.716
Don't worry about it.
Then we will be on our way.

05:37.017 --> 05:41.437
I'm really sorry for the inconvenience.
See you in Yangshuo.

05:43.336 --> 05:48.316
Rest assured. Juemei is good at
taking care of people.

05:49.416 --> 05:50.517
Let's go.

05:55.937 --> 05:57.376
Follow me. Come on.

05:57.376 --> 05:58.176
Is this the one?

05:58.176 --> 05:59.057
This.

05:59.057 --> 05:59.957
Just this.

05:59.957 --> 06:03.257
Why is this only three-star? I saw
a five-star one on the other side.

06:03.257 --> 06:04.336
No, this is the highest rank.

06:04.336 --> 06:05.856
68. A good figure.

06:05.856 --> 06:06.376
Okay.

06:06.376 --> 06:07.477
This one is big and long.

06:07.477 --> 06:09.197
Watch the steps.

06:09.197 --> 06:10.097
Guys.

06:10.097 --> 06:12.077
What great views of the mountains.

06:12.776 --> 06:15.097
Good. Let's take a picture
and show Zhou Zheng.

06:15.097 --> 06:17.117
Hurry up.

06:17.976 --> 06:18.957
Together.

06:18.957 --> 06:20.156
Let's take a picture.

06:22.497 --> 06:23.457
The breeze.

06:23.457 --> 06:24.097
Nice, isn't it?

06:24.097 --> 06:25.536
The breeze is so comfortable.

06:25.536 --> 06:27.036
Come on.

06:27.577 --> 06:28.976
Get on. The boat is about to start.

06:28.976 --> 06:29.997
The weather is good today.

06:29.997 --> 06:32.317
We'll take photos later.
Let's go in first.

06:32.317 --> 06:34.036
Go in.

06:34.036 --> 06:35.517
How beautiful.

06:36.897 --> 06:37.577
Let's go.

06:37.577 --> 06:38.596
Go.

06:38.596 --> 06:39.416
Let's go.

06:39.416 --> 06:40.836
Let's go to our room.

06:41.736 --> 06:42.717
There's air conditioning.

06:42.717 --> 06:47.236
Our room is there. Today, nobody is
on the second floor. Sit anywhere.

06:48.736 --> 06:49.256
It's cool.

06:49.256 --> 06:50.757
There's more inside.

06:51.497 --> 06:53.356
Hear. What you're saying.

06:54.776 --> 06:55.837
Make yourself at home.

06:55.837 --> 06:57.757
This place is good.

06:58.577 --> 06:59.517
The view is good.

06:59.517 --> 07:00.897
It's different.

07:00.897 --> 07:03.397
Just sit here. We'll order
some tea to drink later.

07:14.536 --> 07:16.756
Come on. Don't just sit.
Let's play cards.

07:16.756 --> 07:19.437
Come on. Are you gonna
play cards, Feng Yasong?

07:19.437 --> 07:20.680
Sure. Come on.

07:20.680 --> 07:22.316
Sheng, are you gonna play?

07:22.316 --> 07:23.717
No.

07:23.717 --> 07:26.557
Do you want some snacks?
I'll go buy some.

07:26.557 --> 07:28.076
I'll go with you. Let's go.

07:28.076 --> 07:29.037
Have a seat.

07:29.037 --> 07:31.657
Do you have any new games?
Always the cards.

07:31.657 --> 07:33.157
It doesn't require brain power.

07:33.157 --> 07:34.756
I'll draw first. Come on.

07:34.756 --> 07:35.776
Then my turn.

07:35.776 --> 07:36.837
Shall we go out?

07:36.837 --> 07:37.717
Okay.

07:37.717 --> 07:40.416
- A good hand. You better watch out.
- Draw your cards.

07:40.416 --> 07:42.157
Stop bluffing.

07:42.157 --> 07:43.517
Draw your cards.

07:44.457 --> 07:45.937
A good hand.

07:45.937 --> 07:47.637
Only one.

08:01.257 --> 08:04.956
I heard before the landscape
was incomparable.

08:05.320 --> 08:08.476
It's indescribable.

08:08.476 --> 08:10.177
Let me take a photo for you.

08:10.177 --> 08:11.517
Okay.

08:14.577 --> 08:16.836
Strike a pose. I'll do it.

08:20.617 --> 08:21.717
Is it okay?

08:28.617 --> 08:29.637
How is it?

08:31.017 --> 08:33.717
Do you want to take a photo with me?

08:33.717 --> 08:34.956
Sure.

08:40.617 --> 08:43.517
W-W-Wait a minute.
Let me fix my hair.

08:47.617 --> 08:49.196
The wind's too strong.

08:52.017 --> 08:53.017
Okay.

09:01.176 --> 09:02.916
Make it horizontal.

09:07.416 --> 09:08.977
But if it's horizontal,

09:08.977 --> 09:11.156
we won't capture
the green mountains at the back.

09:13.097 --> 09:14.916
You're right. We can't capture them.

09:16.257 --> 09:17.676
Then just keep it vertical.

09:24.296 --> 09:27.076
Or you could get a bit closer.

09:34.137 --> 09:36.997
Wait. I didn't smile well
in this one. Let's retake it.

09:38.816 --> 09:42.277
Mo Qingcheng, do you want
to take a good photo? Wait. Stop it.

09:42.277 --> 09:43.916
Okay, I'll take good photos.

09:50.476 --> 09:51.597
Look at the camera.

10:16.337 --> 10:21.277
You'd think after seeing other people
in love so much, one would grow numb.

10:21.277 --> 10:25.256
But watching Qiang Qingci fall in love
gets me more and more excited.

10:25.256 --> 10:28.497
It feels a bit like
first love, doesn't it?

10:28.497 --> 10:29.056
Right.

10:29.056 --> 10:30.257
Exactly.

10:30.257 --> 10:31.057
Doesn't it?

10:31.057 --> 10:34.297
Mr. Qiang is naturally innocent,
not like you.

10:34.297 --> 10:35.477
What's wrong with me?

10:35.477 --> 10:37.496
You just look like a playboy.

10:37.496 --> 10:38.896
You don't understand.

10:38.920 --> 10:44.957
Good looks don't equal a wandering eye.
Pass.

10:44.957 --> 10:48.436
I only said you were a playboy.
I never said you were handsome.

10:48.977 --> 10:49.677
You...

10:49.677 --> 10:56.497
He's been single for years. I am not
less popular. Why did I end up alone?

10:56.497 --> 10:59.397
Come on, kid. Show some spirit.

10:59.397 --> 11:00.877
Yeah.

11:02.536 --> 11:03.816
And you throw cards?

11:03.816 --> 11:09.796
Show some spirit! Learn from Zhou Zheng.
He could give up the view for a girl.

11:12.176 --> 11:14.036
Mu, translate for me.

11:15.137 --> 11:16.477
What's he saying?

11:18.816 --> 11:24.237
It's his guess. As far as I can tell,
there's nothing between them.

11:25.337 --> 11:26.537
You're talking about whom?

11:26.537 --> 11:27.797
Sheng's classmate.

11:27.797 --> 11:29.037
The short-haired one.

11:29.037 --> 11:33.116
You didn't notice it, but since they got
on the bus, they haven't been apart.

11:33.116 --> 11:35.537
Quick. The back of the 20-yuan bill.
Let's all go to the deck.

11:35.537 --> 11:36.217
Let's take photos.

11:36.217 --> 11:36.897
The 20-yuan bill.

11:36.897 --> 11:38.257
20 yuan.

11:38.257 --> 11:41.177
Don't disturb them. Let's go upstairs.

11:41.177 --> 11:41.857
Go.

11:41.857 --> 11:42.616
Upwards.

11:42.616 --> 11:44.676
Have some awareness. Don't bother them.

11:47.696 --> 11:52.737
The two mountains on this bill
are right in front. Don't miss them.

11:52.737 --> 11:53.477
- Thanks.
- Thanks.

11:53.477 --> 11:54.684
Not at all.

11:58.576 --> 12:00.197
Are we there?

12:00.197 --> 12:01.517
Where is it?

12:01.517 --> 12:03.517
I guess it's there.

12:03.517 --> 12:04.157
That one?

12:04.157 --> 12:05.577
Not there yet.

12:05.577 --> 12:08.257
- Sheng, come up.
- Come on up.

12:08.257 --> 12:09.137
The view is great up top.

12:09.137 --> 12:09.737
Let's take photos.

12:09.737 --> 12:10.456
You can see it here.

12:10.456 --> 12:11.657
Hurry up.

12:11.657 --> 12:14.176
They've all gone to the top.
Should we go up?

12:14.176 --> 12:15.916
It's windy there.

12:16.696 --> 12:17.996
Okay, we'll go up in a bit.

12:17.996 --> 12:20.077
The higher you stand,
the farther you see. The wind.

12:20.077 --> 12:21.317
Slightly higher.

12:21.317 --> 12:22.077
Let's take a photo.

12:22.077 --> 12:23.116
Come on.

12:23.116 --> 12:24.916
One.

12:26.257 --> 12:27.217
Good.

12:27.217 --> 12:28.397
What?

12:28.397 --> 12:30.397
What a beautiful sky it is.

12:30.397 --> 12:32.776
Come on, everyone takes one each.

12:32.776 --> 12:33.737
Have we arrived, Mr. Zhu?

12:33.737 --> 12:34.257
Let me look.

12:34.257 --> 12:35.417
Where are we?

12:35.417 --> 12:36.257
Just ahead.

12:36.257 --> 12:36.937
Which one is it?

12:36.937 --> 12:38.316
That one!

12:41.497 --> 12:47.417
I haven't used bills for so long.
Do you think in another ten years,

12:47.417 --> 12:52.157
kids will still be familiar
with the 20-yuan bill?

12:52.157 --> 12:53.597
Possibly not.

12:57.897 --> 13:00.457
How come we're not included?
You're excluding us.

13:00.457 --> 13:01.217
Excluding us.

13:01.217 --> 13:02.137
You hold this.

13:02.137 --> 13:04.156
- That's too much.
- Everyone will be captured.

13:04.156 --> 13:05.436
Are you ready?

13:05.436 --> 13:06.377
Cheese.

13:06.377 --> 13:08.357
Cheese.

13:17.576 --> 13:18.077
It's raining.

13:18.077 --> 13:19.757
Why did it suddenly start raining?

13:21.497 --> 13:22.796
You're wet.

13:25.097 --> 13:26.717
Do you want to go inside?

13:27.416 --> 13:28.436
Either is fine.

13:29.776 --> 13:33.556
Just a pity. Who knows
when we'll come here again?

13:35.576 --> 13:37.977
You go inside and wait.
When we're almost there, I'll tell you.

13:37.977 --> 13:38.857
No, you...

13:38.857 --> 13:40.316
You wait inside.

13:47.497 --> 13:48.576
It's raining heavier.

13:48.576 --> 13:49.897
It's too heavy.

13:49.897 --> 13:51.057
How can it rain so much?

13:51.057 --> 13:51.857
It's common here.

13:51.857 --> 13:52.377
Is it that?

13:52.377 --> 13:53.377
It rains frequently here.

13:53.377 --> 13:54.677
It'll stop soon.

13:54.677 --> 13:56.117
Thanks.

13:57.617 --> 14:00.057
Why insist on
waiting outside in the rain?

14:00.057 --> 14:06.197
The real scenes from the bill. Exciting.
Let's take lots of photos later.

14:06.197 --> 14:12.157
There must be lots of pictures online.
Why not just download them?

14:12.157 --> 14:15.577
Mu, being too sensible
can make people dislike you.

14:15.577 --> 14:18.757
I've told him 100 times already.
He's just unromantic.

14:18.757 --> 14:20.457
Get ready to take photos.
We're almost there.

14:20.457 --> 14:24.737
Just take a few. The mountains
all look similar. Photoshop them later.

14:24.737 --> 14:26.056
Got it.

14:26.056 --> 14:28.397
It's raining harder and harder.

14:54.626 --> 14:58.379
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

14:58.379 --> 14:59.559
♪ Depict a stroke ♪

14:59.559 --> 15:00.587
♪ Of rain before the mountain ♪

15:00.587 --> 15:02.986
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

15:03.010 --> 15:07.115
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

15:07.115 --> 15:09.675
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

15:09.675 --> 15:12.159
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

15:13.218 --> 15:16.939
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

15:16.939 --> 15:18.347
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

15:18.347 --> 15:21.436
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

15:21.436 --> 15:22.475
♪ On this journey ♪

15:22.475 --> 15:24.665
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

15:25.137 --> 15:27.257
The rain is too heavy.
You might as well come in.

15:27.257 --> 15:29.276
That's okay. Let's wait a little longer.

15:31.138 --> 15:33.564
♪ Just like ♪

15:34.257 --> 15:37.757
You don't have to. Come in.
It's not necessary to watch it.

15:39.617 --> 15:40.877
Look at that.

15:43.810 --> 15:44.898
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

15:44.898 --> 15:49.371
♪ I could hear you among millions of voices ♪

15:49.371 --> 15:52.346
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

15:52.377 --> 15:53.837
It's raining heavily.

15:55.977 --> 15:59.937
It's exactly the same.
I thought it was imaginary as a girl.

15:59.937 --> 16:01.717
Do you want to take a photo?

16:03.416 --> 16:04.436
Let's do it.

16:06.776 --> 16:07.440
Like this.

16:07.464 --> 16:10.812
♪ Among the millions of people ♪

16:11.137 --> 16:12.922
My hand like this.

16:12.946 --> 16:16.801
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

16:16.801 --> 16:19.512
♪ Tangled love for millions
of dawns and dusks ♪

16:19.536 --> 16:21.416
That's it. Hurry up.

16:21.416 --> 16:22.017
Take a photo.

16:22.017 --> 16:23.217
Mu, come now.

16:23.217 --> 16:25.597
Hurry up. Come here
and take a photo together.

16:26.737 --> 16:27.257
Hurry up.

16:27.257 --> 16:28.217
Come on.

16:28.217 --> 16:28.876
Let's do it.

16:28.876 --> 16:32.357
Three, two, one. Done.

16:32.357 --> 16:35.397
Take a photo for us.

16:45.022 --> 16:46.919
♪ Just like ♪

16:46.919 --> 16:47.849
♪ When the clouds are low ♪

16:47.849 --> 16:49.474
♪ It rains ♪

16:49.474 --> 16:53.938
♪ I was moved
when you were singing softly ♪

16:53.938 --> 16:57.671
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

16:57.671 --> 16:58.759
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

16:58.759 --> 17:03.432
♪ I could hear you
among millions of voices ♪

17:03.456 --> 17:04.317
Dry yourself off.

17:04.317 --> 17:05.996
Such heavy rain.

17:08.736 --> 17:09.877
Here's a towel.

17:09.877 --> 17:11.077
Thanks.

17:16.897 --> 17:17.956
Are you cold?

17:19.617 --> 17:20.676
Let me dry it.

17:23.617 --> 17:25.317
I'm all wet.

17:25.317 --> 17:27.736
Is there hot water
for me to wash my face?

17:27.736 --> 17:28.936
Thinking this is a hotel? Hot water.

17:28.936 --> 17:29.917
The rain.

17:29.917 --> 17:30.976
It's too sudden, isn't it?

17:30.976 --> 17:32.816
This rain is too heavy, isn't it?

17:32.816 --> 17:34.357
This side also got wet.

17:35.377 --> 17:36.676
What are you looking at?

17:42.337 --> 17:44.797
- Let's grab towels.
- Let's grab towels.

17:45.416 --> 17:46.837
- You guys...
- Here.

17:47.577 --> 17:48.337
Here.

17:48.337 --> 17:50.077
I'll get you some hot tea.

17:53.337 --> 17:54.716
Sit down.

17:59.416 --> 18:00.836
Thanks.

18:00.836 --> 18:02.216
Let's sit.

18:02.216 --> 18:04.476
Wait a minute. It's a bit hot.

18:04.476 --> 18:06.357
I'm soaked already.

18:14.416 --> 18:15.416
It's ready.

18:16.176 --> 18:17.196
Thanks.

18:41.097 --> 18:43.357
Sir, could you please
turn up the temperature?

18:43.357 --> 18:44.476
Okay.

18:46.496 --> 18:51.017
You came here, but you're not taking
a boat. You'll miss a lot of scenery.

18:51.017 --> 18:59.017
It was sad to think she'd be alone
in the car with no one's company.

19:03.057 --> 19:04.077
You're awake.

19:06.216 --> 19:10.476
I saw you were sleeping when the car
just stopped, so I didn't wake you up.

19:12.297 --> 19:13.277
What is this?

19:13.277 --> 19:19.277
It's hot milk tea. I was afraid it would
get cold, so I bought a vacuum bottle.

19:21.577 --> 19:23.317
It's raining now.

19:23.936 --> 19:25.456
Didn't you get...?

19:25.456 --> 19:26.877
It's okay.

19:27.617 --> 19:28.837
You have a try.

19:38.377 --> 19:39.137
Is it good?

19:39.137 --> 19:40.797
It's really good.

19:42.857 --> 19:45.756
Of course, it's cooked
from real tea leaves.

19:47.297 --> 19:49.357
Sir, where are you from in Guilin?

19:49.357 --> 19:53.397
I'm from Yangshuo. After I drop you off,
I will go home for dinner.

19:53.397 --> 20:00.257
Stay awake later. When the rain stops,
I'll stop for you to take pictures.

20:00.257 --> 20:07.236
Thank you. I don't care, but it is
her first time on a long trip.

20:33.016 --> 20:33.757
A pair of five.

20:33.757 --> 20:34.917
A pair of five?

20:34.917 --> 20:36.016
A pair of five?

20:36.016 --> 20:36.676
Bomb.

20:36.676 --> 20:38.176
It was just a pair of five.

20:38.176 --> 20:39.377
- Why did you play that?
- Puzzling.

20:39.377 --> 20:40.857
- Let me play this.
- Just messing around.

20:40.857 --> 20:43.097
What's this? Wait.
Why didn't you play a bomb just now?

20:43.097 --> 20:44.217
I'll play one.

20:44.217 --> 20:45.916
He's serving food. Look.

20:46.817 --> 20:50.357
I just asked. It's half an hour away.
Let's have this to kill time.

20:51.537 --> 20:54.196
How can you always find
delicious food wherever you go?

20:55.016 --> 20:57.797
Because many of my friends are foodies.

20:59.057 --> 21:00.077
There's only one dish?

21:00.077 --> 21:00.957
Go get some.

21:00.957 --> 21:02.357
Why don't you get it?

21:03.857 --> 21:05.597
- Here it comes.
- Here it comes.

21:06.297 --> 21:06.877
Let's share.

21:06.877 --> 21:07.556
Thank you.

21:07.556 --> 21:08.557
Thanks, Mr. Qiang.

21:08.557 --> 21:09.736
Thanks, Mr. Qiang.

21:09.736 --> 21:10.617
Let's collect the cards.

21:10.617 --> 21:11.996
Sure.

21:12.736 --> 21:14.217
I'll taste it for you first.

21:14.217 --> 21:16.077
You are really not self-effacing.

21:19.577 --> 21:20.196
How is it?

21:20.196 --> 21:21.916
Yummy.

21:23.582 --> 21:25.088
♪ On this journey ♪

21:25.456 --> 21:26.716
You taste it.

21:28.456 --> 21:28.997
How is it?

21:28.997 --> 21:30.436
Indeed, it's good.

21:34.656 --> 21:35.956
Thanks.

21:36.062 --> 21:38.089
♪ It rains ♪

21:40.297 --> 21:41.997
They live in their own little world.

21:41.997 --> 21:43.876
Why are you always staring at them?

21:43.876 --> 21:45.397
Did you hear that?

21:46.656 --> 21:48.637
Their love song
has been played several times already.

21:48.637 --> 21:53.277
I've also noticed that
and the other songs are related to him.

21:53.277 --> 21:57.377
Either his theme songs or
from the show he provided voiceover for.

21:57.377 --> 22:00.017
Envious? You can sing it yourself.

22:00.017 --> 22:02.436
I can't. I'm tone-deaf.

22:03.736 --> 22:07.877
Don't you feel embarrassed? You are
the real traditional-style singers.

22:08.897 --> 22:10.076
It is a bit shameful indeed.

22:10.076 --> 22:16.076
Yeah, at least we are both well-known.
Doudou, don't you feel anything?

22:16.076 --> 22:19.797
No. Besides, Mr. Qiang's singing
sounds good in the first place.

22:21.097 --> 22:21.857
Wait for it.

22:21.857 --> 22:22.677
What are you doing?

22:22.677 --> 22:23.456
Where are you going?

22:23.456 --> 22:24.497
Ready for battle.

22:24.497 --> 22:27.277
Waiter, can we order songs? Thank you.

22:28.496 --> 22:29.536
Guess which song he will order.

22:29.536 --> 22:34.617
I guess, Cool Break,
White Horse and one of your songs.

22:34.617 --> 22:37.317
I guess the first one
must be White Horse. Let's see.

22:40.256 --> 22:41.077
See?

22:41.077 --> 22:42.237
- You're right.
- Am I right?

22:42.237 --> 22:45.257
I'm done ordering. The rest
are all the songs of us three.

22:45.257 --> 22:47.257
I'm going to eat this serving of snails.

22:47.257 --> 22:50.417
When with you, my mouth never stops.

22:50.417 --> 22:53.117
Don't you ever get bored of just eating?

22:53.117 --> 22:58.756
Of course not! Food comes first.
It's a basic human need.

23:00.736 --> 23:06.637
Many of the dishes here
include snails for added flavor.

23:06.637 --> 23:09.637
If you like them, take the opportunity
to eat as much as you can here.

23:10.577 --> 23:17.277
And the fried prawns. Traveling here
without tasting them would be a pity.

23:17.504 --> 23:19.572
♪ The evening breeze is anxious ♪

23:19.572 --> 23:22.347
♪ Secretly tasting
the fragrance on my collar ♪

23:23.656 --> 23:24.916
Try this.

23:26.456 --> 23:27.656
This is good. Mr. Qiang is generous.

23:27.656 --> 23:28.456
Lijiang River prawns.

23:28.456 --> 23:29.956
Thanks.

23:31.057 --> 23:34.557
Don't fill yourself up.
Eat slowly to pass the time.

23:35.002 --> 23:37.703
♪ Insisting on competing
with the moonlight ♪

23:39.297 --> 23:40.996
- Tasty.
- Tasty?

23:42.297 --> 23:43.560
Grabbing it directly?

23:43.584 --> 23:45.640
♪ Roaming the universe when I'm drunk ♪

23:45.640 --> 23:48.012
♪ Lotus leaves in the lake
and glutinous rice on the table ♪

23:48.012 --> 23:49.992
♪ With a full stomach,
leisurely enjoying the seasons ♪

23:49.992 --> 23:52.334
♪ I have lips and a brush
to record my life ♪

23:52.334 --> 23:54.573
♪ No need for anyone else
to write poems or prefaces ♪

23:54.573 --> 24:02.573
♪ Food witnesses our love ♪

24:02.897 --> 24:04.196
Come. This way.

24:04.196 --> 24:07.157
We've finally arrived.

24:07.157 --> 24:08.417
Look at that.

24:08.417 --> 24:09.277
Right.

24:09.277 --> 24:10.497
They're a bit faster than us.

24:10.497 --> 24:12.777
(Yangshuo, a famous tourist county in China)
A famous tourist county.

24:12.777 --> 24:16.877
Welcome to my hometown, Yangshuo.
Our car is over there. Let's go.

24:16.877 --> 24:17.477
OK, let's go.

24:17.477 --> 24:18.277
Alright.

24:18.277 --> 24:18.997
Let's go.

24:18.997 --> 24:19.997
Let's go.

24:19.997 --> 24:21.576
They have
a water level marker over there.

24:21.576 --> 24:27.297
This year's high tide has just passed.
A concert was held here at the time.

24:27.297 --> 24:29.556
Half of the Yangshuo streets
were flooded. It was quite tragic.

24:29.556 --> 24:31.297
What should you do after the flood?

24:31.297 --> 24:35.457
What could we do? Cleaning it up
and moving on. That's our life.

24:35.457 --> 24:38.317
This is our home, after all. This way.

24:40.137 --> 24:42.637
Come with me. How is it?

24:42.637 --> 24:43.936
The environment is indeed nice.

24:43.936 --> 24:49.836
The best hotel here. It's by the river
and convenient to go anywhere.

24:49.836 --> 24:51.216
Truly magnificent.

24:51.216 --> 24:53.476
It's our tenth anniversary.
We're at the hotel.

24:54.817 --> 24:55.857
Mr. Zhu, this is good.

24:55.857 --> 25:02.357
There are ducks, koi and even alpacas,
and you can feed them.

25:02.357 --> 25:03.057
Alpacas too?

25:03.057 --> 25:04.197
Yes.

25:04.197 --> 25:05.617
Where? I can't see them.

25:05.617 --> 25:08.676
You need to walk further in to see them.

25:09.817 --> 25:11.236
Juemei has arrived.

25:14.377 --> 25:16.797
This lad is so strong.
Look at him, carrying two boxes.

25:18.337 --> 25:22.456
I thought you were trapped by a downpour
and wouldn't come until tomorrow.

25:22.456 --> 25:23.256
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

25:23.256 --> 25:27.757
You're not showing respect to me.
Do you want me to teach you a lesson?

25:27.757 --> 25:28.657
No.

25:28.657 --> 25:30.237
Then who will I share a room with?

25:30.237 --> 25:31.817
Definitely not with me.

25:31.817 --> 25:34.236
How could you even think that?

25:35.016 --> 25:37.476
Actually, Mu is quite a nice person.

25:40.097 --> 25:41.216
Let's pretend I didn't say that.

25:41.216 --> 25:42.917
You're messing around.
I'll leave you guys alone.

25:42.917 --> 25:44.097
Will you two share a room?

25:44.097 --> 25:45.256
Yes, we will.

25:45.256 --> 25:47.916
Then, I will have a room to myself.
What about the three of you?

25:48.976 --> 25:51.297
I'll stay with you, and the two
of them will stay together.

25:51.297 --> 25:52.357
With me?

25:52.357 --> 25:54.437
It's been so long since we last met.
We should chat some more.

25:54.437 --> 25:55.777
Pretending to be decent.

25:55.777 --> 25:58.877
Alright. Let's walk together
and check in. Let's go.

25:58.877 --> 26:00.236
Go.

26:05.537 --> 26:06.956
Is it just ahead?

26:07.897 --> 26:11.156
- The environment is nice.
- It's here.

26:19.857 --> 26:21.477
I've got a sore back
from sitting for so long.

26:21.477 --> 26:23.916
I'm almost stuffed to death from eating.

26:24.456 --> 26:28.196
Weren't you on a boat? How could you
still manage to eat so much?

26:28.196 --> 26:30.464
First, he served me a dish
of river snails.

26:30.464 --> 26:33.418
It's said to be bred in the Lijiang River
and it's fresh.

26:33.418 --> 26:36.677
I didn't finish it
before the second dish is served.

26:36.677 --> 26:44.677
Then came a dish of stir-fried shrimp.
I ate them all so as not to waste them.

26:46.537 --> 26:49.117
You're clearly showing off.

26:51.216 --> 26:54.457
I was hesitating just now.

26:54.457 --> 26:56.357
Hesitating about what?

26:57.456 --> 27:04.137
I was thinking about whether you
wanted to stay with me or him.

27:04.137 --> 27:06.516
Of course, I wanted to stay with you.

27:11.696 --> 27:12.736
What are you doing?

27:12.736 --> 27:15.117
Showering and changing
into summer clothes.

27:24.297 --> 27:29.557
It's not too much for me as a boss
to order a room with a king-sized bed.

27:29.557 --> 27:30.576
Can we change it?

27:30.576 --> 27:31.637
No.

27:32.256 --> 27:37.476
The tourist season and the best hotel.
The rooms were booked up a month ago.

27:46.817 --> 27:47.956
What are you doing?

27:49.416 --> 27:51.277
So narrow.

27:55.297 --> 27:56.397
It can be pulled.

28:00.817 --> 28:03.177
I'll sleep there.
Sorry for the inconvenience.

28:03.177 --> 28:06.196
Call the hotel to get
a new set of bedding.

28:07.656 --> 28:11.197
Why not share a bed? See how spacious.
What are you going to do?

28:11.197 --> 28:12.516
To take a bath.

28:13.456 --> 28:16.196
Seems like you're a clean freak.
Bathing when you get in.

28:18.817 --> 28:20.436
I'm changing clothes. Stay there.

28:29.957 --> 28:31.117
(What are you doing?)

28:41.884 --> 28:44.574
(What are you doing?)

28:45.437 --> 28:46.877
(Waiting for your messages.)

28:52.147 --> 28:54.215
(Waiting for your messages.)

28:58.537 --> 29:00.797
(Does your club have
anything planned for today?)

29:03.456 --> 29:06.436
(Free activities today,
group activities tomorrow.)

29:07.256 --> 29:10.117
(Do you want to go see alpacas?)

29:12.057 --> 29:13.277
(After I dry my hair.)

29:30.833 --> 29:34.863
(I've started location sharing.)

29:39.577 --> 29:43.357
Xiaoxing, I'll go out with Mo Qingcheng.
Don't wait for me tonight.

30:21.577 --> 30:24.077
You're moving so slowly, Sheng.

30:24.077 --> 30:26.277
I can barely recognize you.

30:26.857 --> 30:27.877
Why?

30:28.456 --> 30:30.357
I've never seen you in summer clothes.

30:32.456 --> 30:35.797
That's because we met in the winter.

30:37.817 --> 30:38.837
Try it.

30:47.736 --> 30:49.117
That one is big.

30:50.617 --> 30:52.476
And this side.

31:02.456 --> 31:05.077
Won't they get full
from eating all the time?

31:07.416 --> 31:08.837
That's a good question.

31:09.976 --> 31:15.377
Maybe we can let them digest. Let's go
for a walk before we feed them again.

31:15.377 --> 31:16.716
Okay.

31:20.216 --> 31:21.397
A tandem.

31:22.897 --> 31:24.157
Can you ride a bike?

31:24.157 --> 31:26.824
Yeah, I learned it as a pupil.

31:26.824 --> 31:31.657
But after a fall
when learning riding bikes with my cousin,

31:31.657 --> 31:32.794
I can't get on or off.

31:32.794 --> 31:38.557
I only do it with my foot planted
and choose bikes with the lowest seats.

31:38.557 --> 31:40.236
The lowest.

31:42.936 --> 31:44.297
How many cousins do you have?

31:44.297 --> 31:46.136
Five maternal ones.

31:46.136 --> 31:51.537
And also two paternal ones who are
much older with no common interest.

31:51.537 --> 31:53.617
Are you the only girl in the family?

31:53.617 --> 31:57.277
Yes, it's just me.
So they all call me their treasure.

31:58.256 --> 31:59.397
Treasure?

32:00.617 --> 32:02.277
Everyone dotes on you.

32:03.416 --> 32:10.317
I used to think it was quite good.
I could receive a lot of gifts.

32:10.317 --> 32:15.876
But then slowly, I didn't feel so. They
grew up and all turned like my parents.

32:15.876 --> 32:18.357
So, I got to have many parents.

32:19.416 --> 32:22.856
This time, a cousin even wanted to take
leave to accompany me. Terrifying.

32:22.856 --> 32:24.077
Just give it a try.

32:27.416 --> 32:28.416
Is it okay?

32:30.256 --> 32:34.076
My parents don't have many relatives.

32:34.076 --> 32:37.596
I envy you since I'm usually alone.

32:37.596 --> 32:40.476
No wonder you like being with them.

32:41.057 --> 32:42.097
It's obvious?

32:42.097 --> 32:49.397
You don't speak much, but it can be seen
that you like that lively atmosphere.

32:52.097 --> 32:53.196
Let's go.

32:55.617 --> 32:59.156
Don't ride in front of me.
I'm afraid I'll hit you.

33:02.137 --> 33:06.317
Also, don't ride next to me.
I'll get distracted.

33:06.897 --> 33:07.857
Okay, I will follow you.

33:07.857 --> 33:08.877
Okay.

33:19.337 --> 33:21.777
I read in the description
that that's the Lijiang River.

33:21.777 --> 33:23.716
We can take a bamboo raft and go eat.

33:23.716 --> 33:25.916
Okay, let's scout out the path first.

33:27.817 --> 33:28.696
Slow down on the slopes.

33:28.696 --> 33:29.837
Okay.

33:48.976 --> 33:50.597
Isn't it hot outside?

33:56.097 --> 33:57.717
A calm heart keeps you cool.

33:58.777 --> 34:01.757
Stop pretending.
I know you. What happened?

34:02.576 --> 34:06.596
Those annoying kids are playing mahjong
in my room. I can't even take a nap.

34:07.536 --> 34:09.116
See. I knew it.

34:09.976 --> 34:13.576
Zhou, I want to tell you something.
Haven't I got six sponsors this time?

34:13.576 --> 34:16.797
One of them just withdrew
their sponsorship. It was very sudden.

34:16.797 --> 34:19.157
I knew it wouldn't be good news
when you came to me.

34:21.897 --> 34:23.956
I'll make up for the funding. Carry on.

34:24.817 --> 34:25.697
Rich and generous.

34:25.697 --> 34:26.956
The same to you.

34:31.136 --> 34:32.956
What's her name?

34:38.657 --> 34:39.337
Xiaoxing.

34:39.337 --> 34:42.316
Isn't it hot for you to sit outside?
After a short walk, I started sweating.

34:42.316 --> 34:43.837
Just now, I asked him the same question.

34:43.837 --> 34:46.516
We've ordered high tea inside.
Do you want to join us?

34:47.496 --> 34:49.036
There's air conditioning.

34:50.456 --> 34:53.476
Sure, but how do I get upstairs?

34:53.476 --> 34:54.136
From there.

34:54.136 --> 34:54.777
This way.

34:54.777 --> 34:56.397
Wait for me a moment.

35:00.257 --> 35:02.036
When did you order afternoon tea?

35:02.976 --> 35:05.737
Ordering it now will still be in time.
Just say you insisted on ordering it.

35:05.737 --> 35:07.216
Why are you pinning that on me?

35:07.216 --> 35:10.476
It has to be coincidental. Only then
can she enjoy it without guilt.

35:10.476 --> 35:14.157
When it comes to gentlemen,
you must be mentioned.

35:14.157 --> 35:15.677
Hurry to order food.

35:16.697 --> 35:18.137
- Go.
- You go order yourself.

35:18.137 --> 35:19.797
I'm pulling out funding.

35:20.536 --> 35:22.357
Go. Don't dawdle.

35:22.357 --> 35:23.456
Xiaoxing.

35:23.456 --> 35:24.477
Mr. Zhu.

35:24.477 --> 35:25.837
Go.

35:31.616 --> 35:32.837
You can sit here.

35:47.177 --> 35:48.677
Have you sorted out your things?

35:48.677 --> 35:50.436
Yes.

35:51.136 --> 35:54.177
On such a scorching day,
why were you walking outside alone?

35:54.177 --> 35:59.436
I wanted to take some photos
but I didn't expect it to be this hot.

36:00.897 --> 36:05.476
Quite hot, so I invited you in
to eat something and cool off.

36:12.777 --> 36:18.436
It will be ready soon.
This place serves Western food... Sorry.

36:20.016 --> 36:24.117
Xiaoxing, as one of our partners,
are you satisfied with this hotel?

36:24.117 --> 36:27.537
Yes. This is my first time staying
in such a nice hotel. Thanks.

36:27.537 --> 36:28.956
Zhou Zheng chose it.

36:30.377 --> 36:31.996
A friend of mine recommended it.

36:35.576 --> 36:36.657
The air is nice here.

36:36.657 --> 36:37.757
It's quite refreshing.

36:37.757 --> 36:39.956
My hometown has a good view.

36:43.337 --> 36:47.297
Sometimes, I-I-I just feel homesick
when I'm out of town.

36:47.297 --> 36:48.436
(Why?)

36:52.616 --> 36:54.956
(You need to transfer
the meal expense to me, 250 yuan.)

36:58.857 --> 37:00.476
(Then I won't fund you anymore.)

37:00.476 --> 37:04.996
(Transfer the money and also support me,
or I won't act with you.)

37:06.817 --> 37:08.357
(Serves you right for breaking up.)

37:08.357 --> 37:10.737
Do I interrupt your work?

37:10.737 --> 37:12.636
- No.
- No.

37:22.337 --> 37:23.436
Look.

37:23.976 --> 37:25.596
These ducks are so beautiful.

37:27.297 --> 37:29.556
They're raised for eating.

37:33.857 --> 37:40.996
They're too good-looking to eat.
Don't they look pretty?

37:41.616 --> 37:44.556
Those white ones over there
are for laying eggs.

37:46.857 --> 37:48.837
I won't eat duck for a few days.

38:06.944 --> 38:11.993
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

38:12.992 --> 38:16.331
♪ My heart is racing ♪

38:16.544 --> 38:20.986
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

38:21.010 --> 38:25.625
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

38:26.656 --> 38:29.911
♪ What kind of look ♪

38:30.622 --> 38:34.620
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

38:34.656 --> 38:37.552
♪ Slowly slowly we fall in love ♪

38:37.576 --> 38:40.717
- You ride slower.
- Okay.

38:41.695 --> 38:46.568
♪ Slowly slowly I am with you ♪

38:46.568 --> 38:48.522
♪ I love you ♪

38:48.522 --> 38:51.768
♪ Slowly slowly we fall in love ♪

38:51.768 --> 38:55.029
♪ Slowly slowly I can't leave you ♪

38:55.029 --> 39:00.233
♪ Slowly slowly I am with you ♪

39:00.257 --> 39:01.257
Wait.

39:04.136 --> 39:06.197
Let me go down
to see if the slope is big.

39:11.897 --> 39:13.677
Be careful.

39:17.777 --> 39:19.996
Not very steep. Come down.

39:21.666 --> 39:24.843
♪ Under every starry sky ♪

39:25.794 --> 39:30.152
♪ I want to get closer ♪

39:31.297 --> 39:33.397
When I was young,
I loved riding downhill.

39:35.616 --> 39:36.616
Let's go.

39:42.217 --> 39:43.516
There's a bamboo raft.

39:44.096 --> 39:46.496
Excuse me, can we take a ride now?

39:46.496 --> 39:48.217
How many of you are there?

39:48.217 --> 39:49.077
Two.

39:49.077 --> 39:52.856
Each trip needs four people,
so wait a bit more.

39:52.856 --> 39:53.616
Then let's wait.

39:53.616 --> 39:56.217
We can't start the boat
until there are enough people.

39:56.217 --> 39:57.596
Okay.

39:59.377 --> 40:02.337
It's too sunny here. How about
sitting on the vine chair over there?

40:02.337 --> 40:04.397
Alright, let's go.

40:09.056 --> 40:11.197
Sis, slow down.
There's a big slope ahead.

40:11.197 --> 40:14.757
Hold onto the brakes with both hands,
or you'll be thrown off.

40:15.337 --> 40:20.877
I wouldn't have come with you
if you hadn't begged me. Don't dawdle.

40:22.016 --> 40:26.636
Isn't it almost our anniversary?
Do you want me to go on stage bruised?

40:31.657 --> 40:32.877
Sheng.

40:35.576 --> 40:38.197
What a coincidence. I thought you guys
left the hotel a long time ago.

40:38.197 --> 40:40.157
We're waiting to take the bamboo raft.

40:40.157 --> 40:44.488
We two just went and there weren't
enough people. Now there are four.

40:44.488 --> 40:45.333
Let's get on aboard.

40:45.357 --> 40:46.476
- Let's go.
- Okay.

40:49.377 --> 40:52.657
It's rare to see you dress up, Mr. Mo.

40:52.657 --> 40:56.236
People dress up for the ones they love.
Mr. Mo is no exception.

40:56.236 --> 41:01.596
You two are dressed quite simply, so you
don't have much interest in each other.

41:02.616 --> 41:03.476
He is provoking us.

41:03.476 --> 41:07.177
We've acted as a couple many times.
How can we be disgusted with each other?

41:07.177 --> 41:08.556
She's right.

41:09.657 --> 41:11.837
We should hurry and board
the raft before it gets dark.

41:11.837 --> 41:13.677
Hurry up, Doudou.

41:20.016 --> 41:21.076
Really not interested in me?

41:21.076 --> 41:24.576
You have been influenced by them,
wanting to fall in love?

41:24.576 --> 41:26.197
Me?

41:28.056 --> 41:30.036
I'm pretty good being alone.

42:22.817 --> 42:24.397
We haven't had a rest
like this for so long.

42:24.397 --> 42:28.317
Yeah, I've almost forgotten
what leisurely life is like.

42:29.337 --> 42:31.797
Just the recording studio
and the hospital every day.

42:33.737 --> 42:35.797
Did you two graduate
from the same school?

42:35.797 --> 42:41.277
Yes, we met online during high school.
He later helped me select my university.

42:41.277 --> 42:43.336
And I ended up attending
his university directly.

42:43.336 --> 42:47.596
Mo Qingcheng had a lot of classes,
so I tutored Feng Yasong.

42:47.596 --> 42:49.537
You only taught me math.

42:49.537 --> 42:51.277
So did you get in?

42:52.016 --> 42:52.796
Yes, I did.

42:52.796 --> 42:54.937
Then you're considered my senior too.

42:54.937 --> 42:55.717
That's right.

42:55.717 --> 42:57.177
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

42:57.177 --> 43:00.677
I didn't dare to say, fearing
someone would think I was buttering up.

43:12.697 --> 43:13.697
Look.

43:14.817 --> 43:18.516
Is it hollow down there?
Can I snorkel in?

43:20.257 --> 43:23.756
Yes, it's possible,
but you tourists cannot go down.

43:23.756 --> 43:29.036
What's down there?
Like the stalactite caves in movies?

43:30.056 --> 43:35.837
Roughly, every year when the fishing ban
is over, we often catch fish there.

43:35.837 --> 43:41.157
There are a lot of fish down there.
Hold on tight. The rapids are ahead.

43:41.157 --> 43:42.436
Okay.

43:47.096 --> 43:48.116
Rapids.

44:17.054 --> 44:19.272
♪ In the shade of trees, the frog croak ♪

44:19.272 --> 44:21.505
♪ The pond awakens
from its afternoon dream ♪

44:21.505 --> 44:23.675
♪ The weather is sleepy ♪

44:23.675 --> 44:25.803
♪ Summer sunlight shines the courtyard ♪

44:25.803 --> 44:27.952
♪ Sticky rice is great for the yeast ♪

44:27.952 --> 44:30.407
♪ Waiting until it tastes sweet,
drink with ice ♪

44:30.407 --> 44:32.310
♪ The wine thickens the poetry ♪

44:32.310 --> 44:34.474
♪ The goddess's heart throbbed ♪

44:34.474 --> 44:36.772
♪ Free a boat ♪

44:36.772 --> 44:38.878
♪ Leisurely row across the bund ♪

44:38.878 --> 44:41.105
♪ It has rained suddenly ♪

44:41.105 --> 44:43.334
♪ Wet the lotus ♪

44:43.334 --> 44:45.475
♪ The lotus grow very well ♪

44:45.475 --> 44:47.803
♪ Pour the wine, read an ancient poem ♪

44:47.803 --> 44:49.899
♪ The wind blows ♪

44:49.899 --> 44:53.052
♪ Blowing my lappet ♪

44:54.110 --> 44:56.264
♪ Pomegranate flowers
break the wooden window bars ♪

44:56.264 --> 44:58.504
♪ Basking in the sun,
reigniting the poetic fervor within ♪

44:58.504 --> 45:00.770
♪ Night breeze,
green grass, cicada's chirping ♪

45:00.770 --> 45:02.767
♪ Covering the river
with a blanket of stars ♪

45:02.767 --> 45:05.185
♪ In folly bold ♪

45:05.185 --> 45:07.688
♪ Fireflies aspire to rival
the moon's luminosity ♪

45:07.688 --> 45:11.592
♪ Illuminating everything on my mind ♪

45:11.592 --> 45:13.893
♪ Dreaming of ice and snow in August ♪

45:13.893 --> 45:16.005
♪ Roaming the universe when I'm drunk ♪

45:16.005 --> 45:18.177
♪ The fragrance of cheese,
schools of fish in the river ♪

45:18.177 --> 45:20.237
♪ With a full stomach,
leisurely enjoying the seasons ♪

45:20.237 --> 45:22.440
♪ I have lips and a brush
to record my life ♪

45:22.440 --> 45:25.096
♪ No need for anyone else
to write poems or prefaces ♪

45:25.096 --> 45:32.757
♪ Food witnesses our love ♪

45:33.406 --> 45:35.560
♪ Pomegranate flowers
break the wooden window bars ♪

45:35.560 --> 45:37.823
♪ Basking in the sun,
reigniting the poetic fervor within ♪

45:37.823 --> 45:39.891
♪ The Milky Way hosts visiting carps ♪

45:39.891 --> 45:42.081
♪ A meteor hides in the well ♪

45:42.081 --> 45:44.200
♪ Casting aside the book
and falling asleep ♪

45:44.200 --> 45:46.920
♪ Meeting the season ♪

45:46.920 --> 45:50.856
♪ Enjoying the fireworks of time ♪

45:50.856 --> 45:53.122
♪ Dreaming of ice and snow in August ♪

45:53.122 --> 45:55.236
♪ Roaming the universe when I'm drunk ♪

45:55.236 --> 45:57.484
♪ Brasenia and fish with ice
and home-cooked congee ♪

45:57.484 --> 45:59.531
♪ Tasting the coolness
of the season throughout ♪

45:59.531 --> 46:01.906
♪ I have lips and a brush
to record my life ♪

46:01.906 --> 46:04.481
♪ No need for anyone else
to write poems or prefaces ♪

46:04.481 --> 46:05.608
♪ You and I are joyful ♪

46:05.608 --> 46:13.180
♪ Food witnesses our love ♪
